title: 238: Manning Benched, Why is the Eagles offense clicking?
itunes:title: 238: Manning Benched, Why is the Eagles offense clicking?
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks react the news out of New York that Eli Manning has been benched for Geno Smith. Where do the Giants go from here (1:00)? The guys then welcome longtime college and NFL coach John Lilly to tell you why the Eagles offense is firing on all cylinders (10:20). DJ and Bucky wrap the show by diving into the wild college football weekend and coaching carousel (21:17).
